#: ../docs/source/backup/index.rst:187
msgid ""
"Apart from the database backup, you should also backup the AiiDA repository."
" For small repositories, this can be easily done by a simple directory copy "
"or, even better, with the use of the rsync command which can copy only the "
"differences. However, both of the aforementioned approaches are not "
"efficient in big repositories where even a partial recursive directory "
"listing may take significant time, especially for filesystems where "
"accessing a directory has a constant (and significant) latency time. "
"Therefore, we provide scripts for making efficient backups of the AiiDA "
"repository."
msgstr ""
"除了数据库的备份，AiiDA仓库也应当备份。对小的仓库，这一操作可由简单的复制粘贴完成，或更推荐地使用rsync命令来进行增量复制。然而，这些操作对较大的仓库是不够高效的，因为就连部分递归目录列表的操作都会花去显著的时间，特别是当文件系统访问目录有一个恒定（且重要）的延迟时间。因此，我们提供可以高效地创建AiiDA仓库备份的脚本。"

